FILE: Kanye West won the Grammy for Best Contemporary Christian Music Album for "Jesus Is King". AFP/Angela Weiss JOHANNESBURG - Seems like things are looking good for Kanye West. The musician has made history after it was reported that he has become one of the richest black men in the United States. Kanye West’s net worth has reached $6.6-billion. READ: Kanye wins Grammy for best contemporary Christian album The figure includes the rapper’s Yeezy clothing and a shoe deal with Gap and Adidas. West’s other riches come from his music catalogues and investments. This is a huge comeback for the former presidential candidate, who years ago claimed he was swimming in debt. West had poured his money into his fashion line.